15:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-10 border-l-2 border-white/10 pl-6 italic","children":"The MESIRE Balloon Sinus Dilation System is an advanced, minimally invasive surgical solution designed to open inflamed sinuses. It utilizes a precise, single-use flexible balloon catheter to reach inflamed sinuses and gently inflate to restructure previously blocked nasal passages without the removal of bone or tissue, preserving normal anatomy and mucosal tissue."}]
