1c:T453,Internal evidence and external manufacturer sources consistently describe MESIRE as a complete balloon sinus dilation system for minimally invasive treatment of chronic and recurrent rhinosinusitis. The system includes non-compliant balloons, guide catheters, light wire, and specialized sinus kits for frontal and maxillary procedures. Multiple SKUs confirm this is a product family, not a single device. External Meril manufacturer sources verify the product exists and confirms the balloon dilation mechanism (analogous to cardiac angioplasty) for opening inflamed sinus ostia under endoscopic guidance. No conflicts between internal brochure and manufacturer web evidence. Classification as product_family is appropriate given the complete system nature with multiple components and procedure kits. Material specification (medical grade polymers and stainless steel) aligns with typical balloon catheter construction. Regulatory approvals (Indian DCGI, European CE Mark) verified through manufacturer source. High confidence due to direct manufacturer verification and consistent internal documentation.17:["$","$L1b",null,{"product":{"product_name":"MESIRE Balloon Sinus Dilation System","product_name_display":"MESIRE Balloon Sinus Dilation System","sku_code":"MESIRE-BSD-001","product_family":"MESIRE Balloon Sinus Dilation System","product_family_display":"MESIRE Balloon Sinus Dilation System","slug":"mesire-balloon-sinus-dilation-system","images":[{"id":"446ceabe38c6","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3e6bb39fd4a3825e631a6/cover_3f2b29c5.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Tournisys Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":330271,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:36.291606+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction","width":1654,"height":2339},{"id":"2b9a1455043c","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3e6bb39fd4a3825e631a6/cover_9c3f8b71.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Tournisys Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":330271,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26